{"serial": "43021", "department_serial": 39, "code": "IM4055", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Strategic Management", "ch": "企業政策"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": ""}, "instructor": {"en": ["Li, Shau-Mei"], "ch": ["李小梅"]}, "credits": 3, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 3, "session": ["5", "6", "7"]}, "loc": {"building": "I1", "room": "107"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": 60, "department": {"ch": "資訊管理學系", "en": "Department of Information Management"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "部份使用", "en": "Optional"}, "assigned": 27, "selected": 58, "remark": {"ch": "", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "1. 探討當代新的策略管理來反映當代管理理論與實務的變遷。\n2. 在管理個案上融入當代最新的管理議題，尤其是高科技公司面臨的策略挑戰。\n3. 幫助同學對策略管理引發興趣，產生學習動機，進而體悟策略管理的理論與實務意涵。", "en": "1. To discuss new strategic management theory in reflection of the modern management theories and their practices. \n2. To discuss cases which involved new management issues, especially focus on \nthe strategic challenges of high-tech companies. \n3. To arouse students‘ interest toward strategic management knowledge, and to understand strategic management theories and their practices."}, "outline": {"ch": "1. 策略性領導:策略管理制定程序以塑造競爭優勢\n2. 外部分析:辨識機會與威脅\n3. 內部分析:資源與競爭優勢\n4. 由功能層級策略建立競爭優勢\n5. 由事業層級策略建立競爭優勢\n6. 事業層級策略與產業環境\n7. 策略與科技\n8. 全球環境中的策略\n9. 公司層級策略:水平整合、垂直整合與策略性委外\n10.公司層級策略:相關與非相關\n11.公司治理、社會責任與倫理社會責任與倫理\n12.組織與策略執行", "en": "1. Strategic Leadership: Managing the Strategy-Making Process for Competitive Analysis.\n2. External Analysis: The Identification of Opportunities and Threats.\nPart II: THE NATURE OF COMPETITIVE ADVANTAGE.\n3. Internal Analysis: Resources and Competitive Advantage\n4. Building Competitive Advantage Through Functional-Level Strategy.\nPart III: STRATEGIES.\n5. Building Competitive Advantage Through Business-Level Strategy.\n6. Business-Level Strategy and the Industry Environment.\n7. Strategy and Technology.\n8. Strategy in the Global Environment.\n9. Corporate-Level Strategy: Horizontal Integration, Vertical Integration, and Strategic Outsourcing.\n10. Corporate-Level Strategy: Related and Unrelated Diversification.\nPart IV: IMPLEMENTING STRATEGY.\n11. Corporate Governance, Social Responsibility and Ethics.\n12. Implementing Strategy through Organization."}, "textbook": {"ch": "策略管理，13版，華泰書局", "en": "Strategic Management, 13th Edition, Charles W. L. Hill, Gareth R. Jones, Melissa A. Schilling. 2022, Published by Cengage Learning Asia."}, "selfCompiledRate": {"ch": "30%", "en": "30%"}, "instructMethod": {"ch": "講授\n研討", "en": ["Lecture", "Seminar"]}, "gradMethod": {"ch": "期中考: 50％ \n期末考: 35％ \n課程參與: 15％", "en": "Mid-term Exam: 50％\nFinal Exam: 35％\nClass participation: 15％"}, "officeHour": {"ch": "週三12:00 p.m.-1:00 p.m. 請預約", "en": "Wed. 12:00p.m.-1:00p.m. by appointment"}, "teachWeeks": {"ch": "16+2", "en": "16+2"}, "flexDiscription": {"ch": "教師彈性教學:資料蒐集與個案分析", "en": "Data collection and case study."}, "domain": {"ch": "商管知識\n\n\n、\n\n\n電子商務管理", "en": "商管知識\n\n\n、\n\n\n電子商務管理"}, "map": {"ch": [{"competencies": "管理知識", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "獨立思考和解決問題能力", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "國際觀", "rating": "(5)非常高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "永續發展", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}, {"competencies": "溝通能力", "rating": "(4)高", "assesments": ["紙筆測驗/會考", "口頭報告/口試", "出席/課堂表現"]}], "en": [{"competencies": "Management Knowledge", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Critical Thinking and Problem-solving", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance/Performance"]}, {"competencies": "Global Perspective", "rating": "(5)VeryHigh", "assesments": ["Test/Exam", "Presentation/Oral Exam", "Attendance